Description:
Position Perfect!
Impeccably stylish, immediately inviting and surprisingly spacious, this stunning 1 bedroom apartment is a matter of footsteps from fashion-forward Chapel Street.
Discover a sleek, stone-topped Miele kitchen, far-reaching open-plan living and dining and a private and peaceful balcony with leafy neighbourhood views.
A compelling combination of style, space and security, market entrants and astute investors will appreciate the value and inspect with confidence.
• 1 large bedroom with extensive BIR
• Luxurious bathroom with fully tiled, oversized shower featuring rain shower head
• Handy concealed laundry
• Private access to stunning rooftop garden terrace with Teppanyaki grill
• Moments from trams, South Yarra train station, shopping, Yarra River parkland, schools,
So close to the best of South Yarra, the ILK complex is celebrated for resort-style facilities with exclusive use of pool, gym, cinema and dining room.
For more information, please contact Andrew McCalman today.

Description:
JUST $499,000 - 77 sqm - 2 BED + CAR PARK
Positioned on level five is this bright two bedroom apartment located just off Toorak Road in the heart of South Yarra's cafe and shopping precinct.
Measuring 77 square meters internally this is incredibly priced working out to be just $6,480 / sqm for South Yarra property.
Featuring an extra-large living dining area opening to a deep balcony, huge entertainer's kitchen with island bench, double sink and Euro stainless steel appliances, two queen sized bedrooms with BIRs and external windows.
A sparking bathroom, R/C air conditioning and carpark on title as well as residents' pool, gymnasium and sun deck completes the picture.
Vacant possession available with 60 days notice.

Description:
Northern riverside home with Courtyard
Opposite Darling Park by the Yarra River’s edge, this private two-bedroom apartment set at the very rear of the boutique “Norfolk” complex offers a unique and exclusive living environment where views of the river, a private leafy courtyard and off-street parking on title form the perfect partnership. The setback position provides a wonderful buffer from traffic noise resulting in beautifully quiet interiors that are enlivened with northern light. Freshly painted and carpeted throughout, the apartment is a place of calm in the heart of bustling South Yarra and features a light-filled living and dining room with river views, northern light and access to the leafy courtyard retreat with off-street parking and a sunny separate kitchen. Two bedrooms with built-in robes and a bright bathroom with a shower over a bath complete a richly rewarding lifestyle or investment property with an endless number of amenities at its doorstep. Just a stroll away from trendy Lawson Grove café and across the road from bike and walking trails, you can ride to your CBD work base, walk home from the footy or concerts and enjoy the ease of access to the Royal Botanic Gardens, Tan running track, buses, trams, Toorak Road’s restaurants and train station and trendy Chapel Street from this exclusive and sought-after location on the edge of the city. This is a fabulous chance to live a lifestyle of exclusivity at a fabulous price point!

Description:
South Yarra’s Finest Single Level Residence
Exclusively positioned in South Yarra just a short stroll from the Royal Botanic Gardens this outstanding fully renovated residence combines the best of its Victorian heritage with contemporary design to provide both for privacy and entertainment at the grandest scale. Drawing natural light from the North, this single level residence combines exceptional privacy with substantial accommodation in sun drenched and peaceful surrounds.
A luxuriously large main bedroom with WIR and ensuite, with an additional 2 double bedrooms complement exceptional living spaces which include large lounge and dining room a spectacular kitchen that opens to a Zen inspired garden and a haven for outdoor living.
Appointments include Outdoor fireplace and integrated BBQ, spa, steam room and bathroom.. Along with the study, separate laundry, butlers pantry, basement wine cellar, sub floor hydronic heating, ducted air conditioning, security system, C-Bus lighting control, rainwater storage and watering system.
This exceptional residence is exclusively positioned on the fringe of the CBD within walking distance of Melbourne’s sporting precinct, Chapel Street, Toorak Rd, St Kilda Rd, Domain Village, the iconic tan running track, Fawkner Park, fine dining, trams and close to private schools.. This is a rare opportunity to secure a solid and brilliantly designed home in a tightly held precinct.

Description:
Uninterrupted Views and a Genuine Sense of Space
Inspired by a cutting-edge design, sleek urban aesthetic and clever use of natural light and space, this striking apartment stands out from the crowd. Situated on the second floor of a secure building with lift access and brilliantly located in the heart of South Yarra's fashion, restaurant, cafe and bar district. The apartment itself features uninterrupted views across the west towards the city. Comprising of an open plan kitchen flaunting stainless steel dish-drawer, oven and gas cooktop, lounge/dining zone with split system heating/cooling and glass sliding doors opening to an undercover balcony. The double bedroom with built in robes basks in glorious natural light and the contemporary bathroom offers an oversized shower. Every convenience is attended to with European laundry, basement carspace and a generous storage cage.

Description:
Elegance, Grace and Amazing Space
High on Kensington Hill, a beautiful tree-lined boulevard between Como Park and Chapel Street, this ground-floor two-bedroom apartment’s house size proportions and elegant architecture are made even more inviting by its sun swept northern aspect taking in the communal garden surrounds. Tranquil and inviting, the interior’s generosity of space is evident at every turn. Large windows in the living room frame roses and camelias which features heating and access to a northern balcony cushioned with flowers. Celebrations with family and friends can be enjoyed around the table in the dining room; while the separate granite kitchen is well-appointed with a freestanding La Germania stove, Smeg dishwasher and breakfast bench. Two large double bedrooms each with a wall of floor-to-ceiling robes enjoy a full bathroom with a statement piece freestanding vanity and zoned toilet. This exceptional accommodation is rounded out with a large laundry, polished floorboards, elegant glass French doors and a single carport. The quiet location is the perfect last piece to this lifestyle opportunity that places you so close to Toorak Road trams, Chapel Street’s café and lifestyle scene, parkland, the Yarra’s recreational assets and Hawksburn and South Yarra stations.

Description:
Secure, Serene Northern rooftop views with 2 car parks
A prized address accompanies privileged views in this elevated 6th floor north-facing two-bedroom “London Lodge” apartment. Playing centre stage in this home is a north-facing living and dining room with integrated joinery and a seamless flow to a deep balcony taking in fabulous views across the South Yarra and city skyline. Equal measure is given to the functionality of the separate kitchen which boasts a generosity of size, plentiful storage, granite benchtops, breakfast bar, floorboards and lovely leafy outlooks to the north. Two double bedrooms each with floor-to-ceiling wardrobes take in easterly views over Toorak and are well served by two bathrooms, one tiled in marble and one with European tiles and laundry. The location between Toorak Village and Chapel Street gives residents unparalleled connectivity to all the amazing amenity that makes the area so attractive. There is no shortage of places to shop for the latest fashion, stunning homewares or the finest foods; while parkland and transport options are all close by. Wonderful amenity for ease of living includes a security entrance, lift access, a double carport with roller door buddy storage unit and heating. Elegant, private, peaceful and sun-filled, this impeccable apartment offers a wonderful introduction into cosmopolitan South Yarra.

Extra features include lift access, secure basement car parking and full security entrance.
Walk out the front door to all the delights of Chapel Street and the Jam Factory.

Description:
Contemporary Luxury with Lifestyle Attractions at the Door
Commanding a premier position on the 4th floor of a state of the art complex designed by Elenberg Fraser with interiors by Hecker Guthrie, this luxurious apartment offers contemporary living at its finest, showcasing far reaching views from a sophisticated open plan design framed by floor to ceiling double glazed glass. The stunning gourmet kitchen featuring SMEG cooking and DW flows to a stylish open plan living/dining that seamlessly leads out to an all-weather winter garden/enclosed balcony. The master suite offers mirrored built in robes and a striking ensuite with a separate bath. There is an additional bedroom with built in robes, central bathroom, concealed laundry, undercover parking, heating, cooling, NBN connection, rose gold finishes and block out blinds all within a high security complex with daytime concierge, lift access and intercom. An unbeatable location in the heart of vibrant South Yarra, just moments to the Yarra River, Botanical Gardens, Chapel Street’s cafes, nightlife, shops, supermarket, transport and bike paths, promising the perfect scenario for the lock up and leave purchaser or the savvy investor.

Description:
Sophisticated Secure and Spacious Serenity
Situated in the award winning Mirvac-built SY21 complex’s Chapel Mews and tucked away from the main street, this sensational apartment offers impressive dimensions (over 80 sqm approx.), light-filled interiors and two terraces ideal for outdoor entertaining and enjoyment. Immediately inviting, the L-shaped living and dining domain is accompanied by a smartly appointed kitchen boasting smeg appliances and an integrated Dishdrawer. The bedroom is well zoned with a private terrace and direct access to secluded gardens, sundrenched and spacious, while a central bathroom serves in style. Additional appointments include Daikin split-system heating and cooling, secure entrance, lift access and basement parking. SY21 is a gated community that features beautiful established gardens and piazza, caretaker, SY21 Club including a 25-metre swimming pool, spa overlooking the piazza and an extensive gymnasium. Conveniently positioned in South Yarra’s hub, close to Vogue Plaza, Como Cinemas, Jam Factory, Chapel Street’s world recognised shopping strip, trams, train and The Yarra River precinct.
Insights: 2/3 Chapel Mews, South Yarra VIC 3141 was last sold in 2018 and 161 other 1 bedroom unit in South Yarra have recently been sold.

Description:
Botanic Gardens Precinct Art Deco Haven
Celebrated as one of South Yarra’s finest Art Deco landmarks, Castle Towers c1941, a majestic security development of quality and distinction boasts a spectacular rooftop terrace with 360 degree views, lift access and a grand foyer with intercom entrance. Positioned on the ground floor, the impeccable apartment showcases elegant period features, spacious living spaces and sunlit rooms. Capturing the essence of modern day living whilst retaining endearing character and charm, natural light is a prominent feature with soaring high ceilings and windows along the northern side of the building. The living domain stretches out with a dedicated dining space close to the well equipped kitchen and generous meals zone. Two large bedrooms feature built in robes, the bathroom includes a separate bath plus shower and a full size laundry is a rarity in apartments today. Hydronic heating, an open fireplace, block out blinds, copious storage and a separate toilet add to the comfort. Ready to live in now, this meticulously maintained apartment will beckon those who love being close to the action. Stroll to Fawkner Park and the Botanic Gardens, Domain and Toorak Road trams, shops, restaurants and cafes.
Insights: 8/11-21 Marne Street, South Yarra VIC 3141 was last sold in 2018 and 233 other 2 bedroom unit in South Yarra have recently been sold.
